1. Concatenation of Array 
   Learnt use of vector_name.insert(position[vector_name.end()], new_vector.begin(), new_vector.end())
2. Contains Duplicate
   Instead of making a map, simple make set and check st.count(num)
3. Valid Anagram
   Anagram means 2 strings are same but jumbled. Make 1 list a-z and add and subtract char instances of both strings.
4. Two Sum
   Use maps and complement or vector of pairs then sorting and 2 pointer.
